{
 "name": "RPlog_Garat_and_Stalh",
 "title": "Garat and Stalh",
 "summary": "In a seedy, smoke-filled cantina, New Republic Navy Lieutenant Garat -- a FleetOps officer nursing a pathological hatred of the Empire -- recognizes the crimson-suited Stalh from anti-Imperial rallies and joins him at the bar. Stalh, a coldly menacing diplomat, steers their drinks-and-dancers small talk toward darker matters, musing about who 'has to die.' He reveals he knows Garat wants a certain one-eyed Imperial woman dead and proposes they act on it together, either bringing her to her knees or ending her once and for all. Unsettled but consumed by his own thirst for revenge, Garat sets aside the New Republic's ideals against cold-blooded murder and, his judgment blurred by anger, repeats Stalh's words back to him in agreement. The scene seals a sinister pact between the two against the Imperial ambassador.",
